This directory contains a sample program that will let you edit menu resources.

The program cannot read resources, so it stores menus in .BME files, but it
also writes the menu definition to a resource format file (.MNU)

EDITDLG.CPP   Source for the menu edit dialog
EDITDLG.HPP
GENMENU.CPP   Source for generating the menu resource
GENMENU.HPP
LOADMENU.CPP  Source for reading a menu from a .BME file
LOADMENU.HPP
MENUEDIT.CPP  Main source file
MENUEDIT.DLG  Menu edit dialog
MENUEDIT.H    Menu edit dialog resource IDs
MENUEDIT.ICO  Application icon
MENUEDIT.IDH
MENUEDIT.MID  Menu resource IDs
MENUEDIT.MNU  Menu
MENUEDIT.RC   Resources
MENUITEM.CPP  Soure for MenuItem and MenuItemList
MENUITEM.HPP
MOVEDOWN.ICO  Icon used in pushbutton
MOVEUP.ICO    -"-
PRODINFO.BMP  Product information bitmap
PRODINFO.DLG  Product information dialog
PRODINFO.H    Resource IDs for product information dialog
PRODINFO.HPP  Header file for product information dialog (note: there are
              no source file)
SAVEMENU.CPP  Source for writing a menu to a .BME file
SAVEMENU.HPP
TESTMENU.CPP  Source for the menu test dialog (both as normal menu and popup)
TESTMENU.DLG
TESTMENU.H    Resource IDs
TESTMENU.HPP

Targets:
  menuedit.exe
    editdlg.cpp
    genmenu.cpp
    loadmenu.cpp
    menuedit.cpp
    savemenu.cpp
    testmenu.cpp
    menuedit.rc
